OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Hong Kong will ease its Covid hotel    
OL,6, quarantine requirements for people     
OL,7, arriving from overseas, Chief Executive
OL,8, John Lee said on Monday.               
OL,10,FFrom Friday, those arriving in the city
OL,11,Fwill have to stay at designated        
OL,12,Fquarantine hotels for three days.      
OL,14,FThey will then undergo another four    
OL,15,Fdays of "medical surveillance" either  
OL,16,Fat home or at any hotel.               
OL,18,FCurrently, overseas arrivals have to   
OL,19,Fquarantine for seven days at designated
OL,20,Fhotels.                                
